<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transfer Funds | AgriBank Texas</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:wght@400;700;900&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; background: #f5f1e8; color: #1A1A1A; line-height: 1.6; }
        h1,h2,h3,h4 { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-weight: 700; }
        a { color: #2D5A27; text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { color: #4A7C42; }
        .container { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        .top-bar { background: #2C2416; color: #C4B49A; font-size: 12px; padding: 8px 0; }
        .top-bar-content { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
        .top-bar-left, .top-bar-right { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
        .top-bar-right a { color: #C4B49A; }
        .navbar { background: #2D5A27; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
        .navbar-content { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 72px; }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: #C4A35A; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; }
        .logo-name { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 20px; color: white; }
        .logo-tagline { font-size: 10px; color: #D4BC7E; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
        .nav-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: white; }
        .nav-user { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
        .user-greeting { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px; }
        .user-greeting strong { display: block; color: white; }
        .btn-logout { color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
        .btn-logout:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; }
        .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s ease; }
        .btn-primary { background: #2D5A27; color: white; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #4A7C42; }
        .btn-outline { background: transparent; border: 1px solid #2D5A27; color: #2D5A27; }
        .btn-outline:hover { background: #2D5A27; color: white; }
        .page-header { margin: 32px 0 24px; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 28px; color: #2C2416; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .page-header p { color: #5C5C5C; font-size: 16px; }
        .transfer-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .transfer-form-section { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
        .transfer-type-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; background: white; padding: 8px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; }
        .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 14px 20px; border: none; background: transparent; border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; color: #5C5C5C; transition: all 0.25s ease; }
        .tab-btn.active { background: #2D5A27; color: white; }
        .tab-btn:hover:not(.active) { background: #F5F1E8; }
        .form-card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(44,36,22,0.08); }
        .form-section-title { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #2C2416; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0ECE4; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
        .form-label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #5C5C5C; margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.3px; }
        .form-input, .form-select { width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; transition: all 0.15s ease; background: white; }
        .form-input:focus, .form-select:focus { outline: none; border-color: #2D5A27; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45,90,39,0.1); }
        .form-input::placeholder { color: #8A8A8A; }
        .input-with-icon { position: relative; }
        .input-icon { position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #8A8A8A; font-size: 14px; }
        .input-with-icon .form-input { padding-left: 44px; }
        .form-hint { font-size: 12px; color: #8A8A8A; margin-top: 6px; }
        .form-divider { height: 1px; background: #F0ECE4; margin: 24px 0; }
        .btn-submit { width: 100%; padding: 16px 32px; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; }
        .summary-card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(44,36,22,0.08); position: sticky; top: 100px; }
        .summary-title { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .summary-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0ECE4; font-size: 14px; }
        .summary-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .summary-label { color: #5C5C5C; }
        .summary-value { font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; }
        .summary-total { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 16px 0; margin-top: 8px; border-top: 2px solid #2D5A27; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
        .summary-total .summary-value { color: #2D5A27; font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; }
        .quick-accounts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .quick-account { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
        .quick-account:hover { border-color: #2D5A27; background: #F9FBF8; }
        .quick-account.selected { border-color: #2D5A27; background: #E8F0E6; }
        .quick-account-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: #F5F1E8; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px; }
        .quick-account-info { flex: 1; }
        .quick-account-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
        .quick-account-number { font-size: 12px; color: #8A8A8A; }
        .quick-account-balance { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: #2C2416; }
        .alert { padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 14px; }
        .alert-success { background: #E8F0E6; color: #2D5A27; border: 1px solid rgba(45,90,39,0.2); }
        .alert-error { background: #FDF2F2; color: #A63D40; border: 1px solid rgba(166,61,64,0.2); }
        .hidden { display: none; }
        .wire-info-box { background: #FDF8ED; border: 1px solid #E5D9A8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .wire-info-box h4 { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #8B6914; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .wire-info-box p { font-size: 12px; color: #6B5A1E; line-height: 1.5; }
        .footer { background: #2C2416; color: #C4B49A; padding: 48px 0 24px; margin-top: 60px; }
        .footer-content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .footer-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .footer-logo-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: #C4A35A; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; }
        .footer-logo-text { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; color: white; }
        .footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.8; }
        .footer-column h4 { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: white; }
        .footer-column ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
        .footer-column a { color: #C4B49A; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer-bottom { padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
        .footer-bottom p { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7; }
        .footer-legal { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
        .footer-legal a { font-size: 12px; color: #C4B49A; }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) { .transfer-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .summary-card { position: static; } .footer-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .footer-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="top-bar-content">
                <div class="top-bar-left"><span>📍 Austin, TX</span><span>📞 1-800-AGRIBTX</span></div>
                <div class="top-bar-right"><a href="#">Locations</a><a href="#">Help</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-content">
                <a href="/dashboard" class="logo">
                    <div class="logo-icon">🌾</div>
                    <div><div class="logo-name">AgriBank</div><div class="logo-tagline">Texas</div></div>
                </a>
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="#">Accounts</a>
                    <a href="/transfer" class="active">Transfer</a>
                    <a href="#">Bill Pay</a>
                    <a href="#">Profile</a>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-user">
                    <span class="user-greeting">Howdy,<strong><%= user.name %></strong></span>
                    <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout">Sign Out</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>Transfer Funds</h1>
            <p>Move money between accounts or send wire transfers</p>
        </div>

        <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success">✓ Transfer of $<%= successAmount %> completed successfully!</div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="transfer-layout">
            <div class="transfer-form-section">
                <div class="transfer-type-tabs">
                    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('internal', this)">Internal Transfer</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('domestic', this)">Domestic Wire</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('international', this)">International Wire</button>
                </div>

                <!-- INTERNAL TRANSFER -->
                <form id="internal-form" class="form-card" action="/transfer" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="transferType" value="internal">
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">Transfer Between Your Accounts</h3>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">From Account</label>
                        <select name="fromAccount" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="">Select source account</option>
                            <% accounts.filter(a => a.type === 'checking' || a.type === 'savings').forEach(function(acc) { %>
                            <option value="<%= acc.id %>"><%= acc.name %> (<%= acc.number %>) - $<%= acc.balance.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2}) %></option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">To Account</label>
                        <select name="toAccount" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="">Select destination account</option>
                            <% accounts.filter(a => a.type === 'checking' || a.type === 'savings').forEach(function(acc) { %>
                            <option value="<%= acc.id %>"><%= acc.name %> (<%= acc.number %>)</option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Amount</label>
                        <div class="input-with-icon">
                            <span class="input-icon">$</span>
                            <input type="number" name="amount" class="form-input" placeholder="0.00" min="0.01" step="0.01" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Memo (Optional)</label>
                        <input type="text" name="memo" class="form-input" placeholder="Add a note">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">Complete Transfer</button>
                </form>

                <!-- DOMESTIC WIRE -->
                <form id="domestic-form" class="form-card hidden" action="/transfer" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="transferType" value="domestic">
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">Domestic Wire Transfer</h3>
                    <div class="wire-info-box">
                        <h4>⚠️ Wire Transfer Notice</h4>
                        <p>Domestic wires typically arrive same-day if submitted before 4:00 PM CT. A $25 fee applies per transfer.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">From Account</label>
                        <select name="fromAccount" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="">Select your account</option>
                            <% accounts.filter(a => a.type === 'checking').forEach(function(acc) { %>
                            <option value="<%= acc.id %>"><%= acc.name %> (<%= acc.number %>) - $<%= acc.balance.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2}) %></option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-divider"></div>
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">Recipient Information</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Recipient Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="recipientName" class="form-input" placeholder="Full legal name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Bank Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="bankName" class="form-input" placeholder="Recipient's bank" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Routing Number (ABA)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="routingNumber" class="form-input" placeholder="9 digits" pattern="[0-9]{9}" maxlength="9" required>
                            <p class="form-hint">9-digit bank routing number</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Account Number</label>
                            <input type="text" name="accountNumber" class="form-input" placeholder="Recipient account #" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Amount</label>
                        <div class="input-with-icon">
                            <span class="input-icon">$</span>
                            <input type="number" name="amount" class="form-input" placeholder="0.00" min="0.01" step="0.01" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Memo / Reference</label>
                        <input type="text" name="memo" class="form-input" placeholder="Payment reference">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">Send Domestic Wire ($25 fee)</button>
                </form>

                <!-- INTERNATIONAL WIRE -->
                <form id="international-form" class="form-card hidden" action="/transfer" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="transferType" value="international">
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">International Wire Transfer</h3>
                    <div class="wire-info-box">
                        <h4>🌍 International Wire Notice</h4>
                        <p>International wires require SWIFT/BIC codes. Delivery takes 1-5 business days. A $45 fee applies per transfer. Additional intermediary bank fees may apply.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">From Account</label>
                        <select name="fromAccount" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="">Select your account</option>
                            <% accounts.filter(a => a.type === 'checking').forEach(function(acc) { %>
                            <option value="<%= acc.id %>"><%= acc.name %> (<%= acc.number %>) - $<%= acc.balance.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2}) %></option>
                            <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-divider"></div>
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">Recipient Information</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Recipient Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="recipientName" class="form-input" placeholder="Full legal name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Recipient Country</label>
                            <select name="country" class="form-select" required>
                                <option value="">Select country</option>
                                <option value="MX">Mexico</option>
                                <option value="CA">Canada</option>
                                <option value="GB">United Kingdom</option>
                                <option value="DE">Germany</option>
                                <option value="FR">France</option>
                                <option value="JP">Japan</option>
                                <option value="CN">China</option>
                                <option value="AU">Australia</option>
                                <option value="BR">Brazil</option>
                                <option value="IN">India</option>
                                <option value="OTHER">Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Bank Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="bankName" class="form-input" placeholder="Recipient's bank" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Bank Address</label>
                            <input type="text" name="bankAddress" class="form-input" placeholder="Bank's street address">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">SWIFT / BIC Code</label>
                            <input type="text" name="swiftCode" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., BOFAUS3N" pattern="[A-Z0-9]{8,11}" maxlength="11" required style="text-transform: uppercase;">
                            <p class="form-hint">8 or 11 character bank identifier</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">IBAN (if applicable)</label>
                            <input type="text" name="iban" class="form-input" placeholder="International account number">
                            <p class="form-hint">Leave blank if not known</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Account Number</label>
                        <input type="text" name="accountNumber" class="form-input" placeholder="Recipient account number" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-divider"></div>
                    <h3 class="form-section-title">Transfer Details</h3>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Amount (USD)</label>
                            <div class="input-with-icon">
                                <span class="input-icon">$</span>
                                <input type="number" name="amount" class="form-input" placeholder="0.00" min="0.01" step="0.01" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Purpose of Transfer</label>
                            <select name="purpose" class="form-select" required>
                                <option value="">Select purpose</option>
                                <option value="family">Family Support</option>
                                <option value="business">Business Payment</option>
                                <option value="purchase">Property Purchase</option>
                                <option value="investment">Investment</option>
                                <option value="services">Services Payment</option>
                                <option value="other">Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Memo / Reference</label>
                        <input type="text" name="memo" class="form-input" placeholder="Payment reference">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">Send International Wire ($45 fee)</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!-- SUMMARY SIDEBAR -->
            <div class="summary-card">
                <h3 class="summary-title">Your Accounts</h3>
                <div class="quick-accounts">
                    <% accounts.filter(a => a.type === 'checking' || a.type === 'savings').forEach(function(acc) { %>
                    <div class="quick-account">
                        <div class="quick-account-icon"><%= acc.icon %></div>
                        <div class="quick-account-info">
                            <div class="quick-account-name"><%= acc.name %></div>
                            <div class="quick-account-number"><%= acc.number %></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quick-account-balance">$<%= acc.balance.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2}) %></div>
                    </div>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
                <div class="form-divider"></div>
                <h3 class="summary-title">Transfer Limits</h3>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">Daily Limit</span><span class="summary-value">$50,000.00</span></div>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">Single Transfer</span><span class="summary-value">$25,000.00</span></div>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">International Daily</span><span class="summary-value">$10,000.00</span></div>
                <div class="form-divider"></div>
                <h3 class="summary-title">Wire Fees</h3>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">Domestic Wire</span><span class="summary-value">$25.00</span></div>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">International Wire</span><span class="summary-value">$45.00</span></div>
                <div class="summary-row"><span class="summary-label">Internal Transfer</span><span class="summary-value">Free</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-brand">
                    <div class="footer-logo"><div class="footer-logo-icon">🌾</div><span class="footer-logo-text">AgriBank Texas</span></div>
                    <p>Serving Texas farmers, ranchers, and families since 1923. Member FDIC.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-column"><h4>Banking</h4><ul><li><a href="#">Checking</a></li><li><a href="#">Savings</a></li><li><a href="#">Loans</a></li></ul></div>
                <div class="footer-column"><h4>Support</h4><ul><li><a href="#">Help Center</a></li><li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li></ul></div>
                <div class="footer-column"><h4>Company</h4><ul><li><a href="#">About Us</a></li><li><a href="#">Careers</a></li></ul></div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>© 2024 AgriBank Texas. All rights reserved.</p>
                <div class="footer-legal"><a href="#">Privacy</a><a href="#">Terms</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function showTab(tab, btnElement) {
            // Hide all forms
            document.querySelectorAll('.form-card').forEach(function(form) {
                form.classList.add('hidden');
            });
            
            // Remove active class from all buttons
            document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
                btn.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            // Show selected form
            var selectedForm = document.getElementById(tab + '-form');
            if (selectedForm) {
                selectedForm.classList.remove('hidden');
            }
            
            // Add active class to clicked button
            if (btnElement) {
                btnElement.classList.add('active');
            }
        }

        document.querySelectorAll('.quick-account').forEach(function(el) {
            el.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.querySelectorAll('.quick-account').forEach(function(a) {
                    a.classList.remove('selected');
                });
                this.classList.add('selected');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>